content: Hey you CMI gurus out there, how to fix "The configuration blabla is not owned by any module."? What is expected? The config file contains a "_module" hint.
Was a module removed and config still existed?
Or a module no longer had a config_info hook?
No, I added a brand new config file. Here's the failing test: https://zen.ci/backdrop/backdrop/test/test-php53-backdrop_backdrop_3163-39a00de
